Hypervisor - software to run several virtual machines
ex: vmware, virtualbox, xen, parallels, proxmox

host os, hypervisor is app on top, inside hypervisor are virtual machines
have to lock down host, only want connections to virtual machines
just shut down networking in host os
use virtualbox ose (open source edition)

